| Intel CPU microcode | Redistributable | https://github.com/intel/Intel-Linux-Processor-Microcode-Data-Files |

*Note: linux-firmware contains various proprietary firmware binaries with redistribution licenses. See WHENCE file in linux-firmware repository for details.

